 source terms, Journal of Computational Physics 86 (1) (1990) 187-210], the relaxation system of Jin and Xin [S. Jin, Z. Xin, The relaxation schemes for systems of conservation laws in arbitrary space dimensions, Communications on Pure and Applied Mathematics 48 (1995) 235-277] and the full compressible Euler equations with stiff friction source terms. ?? 2007 Elsevier Inc. All rights reserved.},
